race.comment: ATLANTIC RAIN (5) debuts for the high-striking Taylor yard with Wiggins a key jockey engagement. Owns a comfortable 1000m trial win at the track and finds a winnable assignment. VIKING SUN (3) has race form/fitness and is the threat. Impressed beaten 1L here two back and was outgraded a touch at Mackay last time but worked home soundly. OH PRETTY EMMA (7) wasn't beaten far at Toowoomba first-up and will be better for it. Tilley is a positive jockey engagement and she can go on with it. ASK ME HARRY (4) has the rail and some gear changes and is a chance going on her placing here two back. Didn't have the best of it last time over a bit longer.
